  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will test whether treatment with N-acetyl-L-cysteine (NAC) is safe and decreases
      pain in patients with chronic neuropathic pain. The investigators hypothesize that NAC will
      be a useful adjunct to opioid treatment in chronic neuropathic pain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is an open-label study to evaluate the safety and efficacy of N-acetyl-L-cysteine in
      patients with Chronic neuropathic pain.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
